<br>
   Also Edano, there was a time (&lt;58) when you didn't have TPP.  For the sake of this thread though, I'd like to leave TPP out and just look at <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Phantom armor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Phantasmal Armor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  The way I see it, Phantasmal is a total waste of a spell for such an expensive reagent and a higher casting level.  I'd like to debate a way to improve it without it stacking with TPP or otherwise disturbing game balance so we can forward it up to VI without suggesting something as ludicrous as Manaburn and a 50% heal *cough* Druids grove *cough*.  <br>
